      "description": "Hindura simulator ku apply CSS yungura ku urupapuro behind iki laboratwari. laboratwari itself stays unfiltered so wowe irashobora keep gukoresha these controls. Kanda tile ku bashisha; kanda again ku hagarika. Only one simulator runs at time.",
      "framing_strong": "Important framing:",
      "framing_body": "simulators ni imperfect approximations. They ni useful kuri empathy-building na byihuse checks, ntibi kuri verifying compliance. protanopia yungura ni ntibi kimwe as protanopia. Real users have lived hamwe na their condition; wowe ni seeing it kuri 60 amasegonda. Koresha simulators ku surface obvious ibibazo (ibara-only amakuru, low contrast, illegible inyandiko), then ikizamini hamwe na real users igihe stakes matter.",
